  "detailed_description": "<h1>Upcoming game</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805990/extras/549f4bd19fd78919b1396ecf22011d04.poster.avif?t=1722704168\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805990/extras/549f4bd19fd78919b1396ecf22011d04.webm?t=1722704168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805990/extras/549f4bd19fd78919b1396ecf22011d04.mp4?t=1722704168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Sinopsis:</strong><br><br>You are Fubuki GORO. You have been trained since your childhood in order to become a deadly kunoichi of the GORO clan.<br>You are employed by the government in the Special Action Agency SAA. They send you anywhere they need to elimainate a threat to the government.<br><br>Today, you have a new mission:<br>Eliminate Elon DUSK, the CEO of EXE company. He is leading some dangerous experimentation on humans, modifying the DNA in order to create super soldiers.<br>The government has asked multiple time to stop and close the facility but DUSK want to go further and further to the end of his objective.<br><br>Therefore, the government has no hope and order the SAA to eliminate DUSK and all the dangerous persons you will encounter in the facility.<br><br>The facility is positioned in a place unknown but we know that you will find it!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805990/extras/b01dfabd0451bff141cdc5da1f6dbc65.poster.avif?t=1722704168\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805990/extras/b01dfabd0451bff141cdc5da1f6dbc65.webm?t=1722704168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805990/extras/b01dfabd0451bff141cdc5da1f6dbc65.mp4?t=1722704168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><br>The gameplay:</strong><br><br>It is all about action. You will use your keyboard and your mouse and mainly your mouse to manipulate Fubuki.<br>The action is very fast paced with a large diversity of enemies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805990/extras/bf444fdb4eba88ae270251b9b35f0694.poster.avif?t=1722704168\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805990/extras/bf444fdb4eba88ae270251b9b35f0694.webm?t=1722704168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805990/extras/bf444fdb4eba88ae270251b9b35f0694.mp4?t=1722704168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>At the end of the game, you will meet Elon DUSK and we already know that he have been \"upgraded\"!<br><br>Use your famous Goro Taijutsu and your special techniques using your shakra but beware not to tired yourself too quickly as it could sign your death!<br><br>A challenge mode is available at any moment. When you will reach a certain level, you will be ready for the \"challenge\".<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805990/extras/506c95b0d1342b40448331475ea2a317.poster.avif?t=1722704168\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805990/extras/506c95b0d1342b40448331475ea2a317.webm?t=1722704168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805990/extras/506c95b0d1342b40448331475ea2a317.mp4?t=1722704168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805990/extras/549f4bd19fd78919b1396ecf22011d04.poster.avif?t=1722704168\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805990/extras/549f4bd19fd78919b1396ecf22011d04.webm?t=1722704168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805990/extras/549f4bd19fd78919b1396ecf22011d04.mp4?t=1722704168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Sinopsis:</strong><br><br>You are Fubuki GORO. You have been trained since your childhood in order to become a deadly kunoichi of the GORO clan.<br>You are employed by the government in the Special Action Agency SAA. They send you anywhere they need to elimainate a threat to the government.<br><br>Today, you have a new mission:<br>Eliminate Elon DUSK, the CEO of EXE company. He is leading some dangerous experimentation on humans, modifying the DNA in order to create super soldiers.<br>The government has asked multiple time to stop and close the facility but DUSK want to go further and further to the end of his objective.<br><br>Therefore, the government has no hope and order the SAA to eliminate DUSK and all the dangerous persons you will encounter in the facility.<br><br>The facility is positioned in a place unknown but we know that you will find it!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805990/extras/b01dfabd0451bff141cdc5da1f6dbc65.poster.avif?t=1722704168\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805990/extras/b01dfabd0451bff141cdc5da1f6dbc65.webm?t=1722704168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805990/extras/b01dfabd0451bff141cdc5da1f6dbc65.mp4?t=1722704168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><br>The gameplay:</strong><br><br>It is all about action. You will use your keyboard and your mouse and mainly your mouse to manipulate Fubuki.<br>The action is very fast paced with a large diversity of enemies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805990/extras/bf444fdb4eba88ae270251b9b35f0694.poster.avif?t=1722704168\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805990/extras/bf444fdb4eba88ae270251b9b35f0694.webm?t=1722704168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805990/extras/bf444fdb4eba88ae270251b9b35f0694.mp4?t=1722704168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>At the end of the game, you will meet Elon DUSK and we already know that he have been \"upgraded\"!<br><br>Use your famous Goro Taijutsu and your special techniques using your shakra but beware not to tired yourself too quickly as it could sign your death!<br><br>A challenge mode is available at any moment. When you will reach a certain level, you will be ready for the \"challenge\".<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805990/extras/506c95b0d1342b40448331475ea2a317.poster.avif?t=1722704168\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805990/extras/506c95b0d1342b40448331475ea2a317.webm?t=1722704168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805990/extras/506c95b0d1342b40448331475ea2a317.mp4?t=1722704168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
